woman who was killed.
 

00:18:27.538 --> 00:18:32.328
Did you--was that--not in your
reading yet.

00:18:32.328 --> 00:18:36.769
What it is, that a Palestinian
woman was suspected of some

00:18:36.769 --> 00:18:39.656
infidelity,
no hard evidence for it,

00:18:39.656 --> 00:18:44.151
and her little brother killed
