00:18:44.151 --> 00:18:45.200
many years.
 

00:18:45.200 --> 00:18:49.368
The idea of giving you that
article is it's a tear jerker,

00:18:49.368 --> 00:18:56.440
but it gives you an idea of the
emotionality of the--

00:18:56.440 --> 00:18:59.532
strength with which the older
social norms are held and

00:18:59.532 --> 00:19:01.710
someone who appears on the
surface,

00:19:01.710 --> 00:19:05.470
even mildly,
to violate it,

00:19:05.470 --> 00:19:07.930
can get killed.
 

00:19:07.930 --> 00:19:14.240
A Jordanian woman has just come
out with a book 2003,

00:19:14.240 --> 00:19:16.835
Honor Lost,
and she talked about her best

00:19:16.835 --> 00:19:19.099
friend and this is what
triggered her,

00:19:19.099 --> 00:19:20.608
apparently, to write the book.
 

00:19:20.608 --> 00:19:23.855
This woman, her friend,
had been seen in public walking

00:19:23.855 --> 00:19:26.019
with a man who was not a
relative.

00:19:26.019 --> 00:19:28.269
Now not doing anything bad but
right there in public,

00:19:28.269 --> 00:19:33.490
so you know nothing was going
on on the streets and this being

00:19:33.490 --> 00:19:36.664
seen alone--
being seen on the streets with

00:19:36.664 --> 00:19:40.615
a man who was not a relative was
such a stain on the family's

00:19:40.615 --> 00:19:44.301
honor that the woman's father
