malnutrition.

00:31:10.480 --> 00:31:12.338
That's a huge number.
 

00:31:12.338 --> 00:31:16.907
That's nine million deaths a
year and so I calculated it out,

00:31:16.907 --> 00:31:21.249
during the course of this
lecture 1,300 people will die of

00:31:21.249 --> 00:31:23.609
starvation or malnutrition.
 

00:31:23.609 --> 00:31:26.950
It's really very serious.
 

00:31:26.950 --> 00:31:28.278
Most of the death--yeah?
 

00:31:28.278 --> 00:31:29.906
Student:  How many
