lecture?
 

00:31:30.220 --> 00:31:31.160
Prof: What?
 

00:31:31.160 --> 00:31:33.518
Student:  How many
people will be born during this

00:31:33.518 --> 00:31:33.940
lecture?
 

00:31:33.940 --> 00:31:36.578
Prof: Also a very large
