three times,

00:31:44.019 --> 00:31:45.288
two and a half times the death
rate,

00:31:45.288 --> 00:31:49.279
but that's not just that--you
can sort of double the total

00:31:49.279 --> 00:31:52.920
number of deaths will be
something a little more than

00:31:52.920 --> 00:31:55.789
double the deaths from
malnutrition,

00:31:55.789 --> 00:31:56.670
so a lot.
 

00:31:56.670 --> 00:32:00.306
The population is still growing
I'll bet, as you've seen,

